          "source_html": "<div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>Questions 27 – 32</strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">The text has six sections. Choose the correct heading for each section and move it into the gap.</p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"word-bank-container\">\r\n        <div class=\"wb-title\">Options (Word Bank):</div>\r\n        <div class=\"wb-grid\">\r\n            <div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>A.</strong> Asian need for new space technology</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>B.</strong> Independence through the greater adaptability of satellites</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>C.</strong> Ancient inventions linked to the future</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>D.</strong> An early start but slow initial progress</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>E.</strong> Non-technical factors affecting Asia's entry to the space age</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>F.</strong> Application of rocket technology to warfare</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>G.</strong> New and wide-ranging uses of space technology</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>H.</strong> The difficulty of identifying types of satellites</div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">27</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_27\" id=\"opt_27_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q27\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_27_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> Asian need for new space technology</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_27\" id=\"opt_27_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q27\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_27_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> Independence through the greater adaptability of satellites</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_27\" id=\"opt_27_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q27\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_27_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> Ancient inventions linked to the future</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_27\" id=\"opt_27_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q27\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_27_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> An early start but slow initial progress</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_27\" id=\"opt_27_E\" data-zyz-question=\"q27\" value=\"E\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_27_E\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>E.</strong> Non-technical factors affecting Asia's entry to the space age</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_27\" id=\"opt_27_F\" data-zyz-question=\"q27\" value=\"F\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_27_F\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>F.</strong> Application of rocket technology to warfare</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_27\" id=\"opt_27_G\" data-zyz-question=\"q27\" value=\"G\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_27_G\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>G.</strong> New and wide-ranging uses of space technology</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_27\" id=\"opt_27_H\" data-zyz-question=\"q27\" value=\"H\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_27_H\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>H.</strong> The difficulty of identifying types of satellites</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> <span class=\"ans-tag\">27</span> C. Ancient inventions linked to the future&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"ans-tag\">28</span> A. Asian need for new space technology&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"ans-tag\">29</span> G. New and wide-ranging uses of space technology&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"ans-tag\">30</span> D. An early start but slow initial progress&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"ans-tag\">31</span> B. Independence through the greater adaptability of satellites&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"ans-tag\">32</span> E. Non-technical factors affecting Asia's entry to the space age</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\">\r\n                <div class=\"sub-analysis-item\">\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-title\">Question 27</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-content\"><p>原文A段讲到了古代中国火箭技术的进步，并且提到了近年来空间活动的增长以及预测了亚洲将成为太空服务的主要提供者。</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <div class=\"sub-analysis-item\">\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-title\">Question 28</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-content\"><p>原文B段首句讲到在世界范围内空间技术有了巨大的发展，亚洲国家热切地接受了这些发展，它们发现这些技术特别适用于它们的特殊问题，即表明亚洲对新的空间技术的需求。</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <div class=\"sub-analysis-item\">\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-title\">Question 29</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-content\"><p>原文C段首句提到不断探索卫星富有想象力和创新性的应用，后文举例应用于医疗、远程教育、农业等领域，表明涉及范围广。<br/></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <div class=\"sub-analysis-item\">\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-title\">Question 30</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-content\"><p>原文D段提到几十年来日本一直是亚洲太空领域的主导力量，表明日本起步早；然而不得不面对严重的耗时的技术挑战和通过许多试验的高风险，表明这个过程很困难，进展缓慢。<br/></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <div class=\"sub-analysis-item\">\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-title\">Question 31</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-content\"><p>原文E段说 “小卫星”为亚洲国家提供了发展低成本卫星技术和迅速建立自己的太空能力的途径，其中 establish a space capability of their own就是选项ii中的independence，且后文小卫星不同质量的分类体现出它能适应更多的应用环境。<br/></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <div class=\"sub-analysis-item\">\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-title\">Question 32</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"sa-content\"><p>原文提到了教育、文化、历史等会影响实践，这些都是非技术因素，会影响亚洲国家进入空间领域的进程。<br/></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>Questions 33 - 36</strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Choose the correct answer to accurately complete the sentence.</p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"word-bank-container\">\r\n        <div class=\"wb-title\">Options (Word Bank):</div>\r\n        <div class=\"wb-grid\">\r\n            <div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>A.</strong> they are seeking plants with medicinal value.</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>B.</strong> they can take pictures of any area required.</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>C.</strong> they depend on what has happened in the past.</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>D.</strong> they do not take up a lot of space aboard rockets.</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>E.</strong> they have locations that are difficult to reach.</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>F.</strong> they help students with their studies.</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>G.</strong> they suffer from such things as forest fires.</div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">33</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><strong>Southeast Asian countries wish to photograph vegetation from above because</strong></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> they are seeking plants with medicinal value.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> they can take pictures of any area required.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> they depend on what has happened in the past.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> they do not take up a lot of space aboard rockets.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_E\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"E\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_E\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>E.</strong> they have locations that are difficult to reach.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_F\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"F\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_F\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>F.</strong> they help students with their studies.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_G\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"G\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_G\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>G.</strong> they suffer from such things as forest fires.</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> G. they suffer from such things as forest fires.</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p>原文B段提到遥感卫星提供了有关自然地表覆盖和种植作物的基本信息，有助于环境管理、灾害预防和可持续规划方面的工作。</p><p><br/></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n    <div class=\"word-bank-container\">\r\n        <div class=\"wb-title\">Options (Word Bank):</div>\r\n        <div class=\"wb-grid\">\r\n            <div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>A.</strong> they are seeking plants with medicinal value.</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>B.</strong> they can take pictures of any area required.</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>C.</strong> they depend on what has happened in the past.</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>D.</strong> they do not take up a lot of space aboard rockets.</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>E.</strong> they have locations that are difficult to reach.</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>F.</strong> they help students with their studies.</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>G.</strong> they suffer from such things as forest fires.</div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">34</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><strong>Asian countries are interested in advances in medical treatment using satellite technology because</strong></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_34\" id=\"opt_34_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q34\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_34_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> they are seeking plants with medicinal value.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_34\" id=\"opt_34_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q34\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_34_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> they can take pictures of any area required.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_34\" id=\"opt_34_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q34\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_34_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> they depend on what has happened in the past.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_34\" id=\"opt_34_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q34\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_34_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> they do not take up a lot of space aboard rockets.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_34\" id=\"opt_34_E\" data-zyz-question=\"q34\" value=\"E\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_34_E\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>E.</strong> they have locations that are difficult to reach.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\