            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_37\" id=\"opt_37_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q37\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_37_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> FALSE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_37\" id=\"opt_37_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q37\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_37_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> B. FALSE</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p>题干说公元前500年，火箭在中国被用于战争， 但原文说的是公元1232年，宋朝在开封之战中首次使用火箭击退侵略者，500BC的时候是使用fireworks。</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">38</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><strong>The distance between satellites and antennas on Earth can be used to detect movement in the Earth&#39;s crust.</strong></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_38\" id=\"opt_38_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q38\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_38_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> TRUE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_38\" id=\"opt_38_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q38\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_38_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> FALSE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_38\" id=\"opt_38_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q38\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_38_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> A. TRUE</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p>题目说地球上的卫星和天线之间的距离可以用来探测地壳的运动，原文C段提到全球定位系统每15秒测量一次天线和卫星之间的距离，这些数据被传输到全球200个监测站中的一个，为地震预测提供了宝贵的持续信息流。两者表述一致，答案为TRUE。</p><p><br/></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">39</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><strong>Distance education has increased literacy levels in Asia.</strong></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_39\" id=\"opt_39_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q39\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_39_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> TRUE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_39\" id=\"opt_39_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q39\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_39_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> FALSE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_39\" id=\"opt_39_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q39\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_39_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> C. NOT GIVEN</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p>题目说远程教育提高了亚洲的识字率，原文C段只提到远程教育项目也取得了有益的进展，并未说亚洲的识字率的情况。</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">40</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><strong>Commercial competition prevents technological innovation spreading.</strong></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_40\" id=\"opt_40_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q40\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_40_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> TRUE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_40\" id=\"opt_40_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q40\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_40_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> FALSE</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_40\" id=\"opt_40_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q40\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_40_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> B. FALSE</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p>题目说商业竞争阻碍了技术创新的传播，根据原文F段首句可知，竞争性的商业部门及其生产的低成本微型卫星促进了亚洲的空间技术，要注意facilitate的意思是促进、推动。</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </di